quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  37,139,Kanti noYûnus wayengomnye wabaThunywa
  37,140,Xa wabalekela kwinqanawa eyayinomthwalo
  37,141,"Wavuma ke ukwenza amaqashiso, waza waba ngomnye wabo balahlekelwayo"
  37,142,Ke kaloku intlanzi enkulu yamginya njengoko wayenze isenzo esigxekekileyo
  37,143,Ukuba ngaba wayengazanga abe ngomnye wabo bazukisa uAllâh
  37,144,Inene yena wayeza kuhlala esiswini sentlanzi de kube yimini yoVuko
  37,145,Kodwa Samphosela elunxwemeni egula enjalo
  37,146,Ke kaloku Sahlumisa umthi womhlavuthwa phezu kwakhe (ngentla kwakhe)
  37,147,Kananjalo Samthumela kubantu abangamawaka aliwaka nangaphezulu kunoko
  37,148,Bakholwa ke; Saza Sabanika ulonwabo lokwethutyana
  37,149,"Ngoku ke khawubabuze (Muhammad): “Ingaba ziintombi5 (zodwa) na Enazo iNkosi yakho baze bona babe noonyana na?”"
  37,150,"Okanye\tmhlawumbi\t(bathi)\tSadala\tiingelosi\tzaba ngabasetyhini lo gama babebukele bona kusini na"
  37,151,Inene kungobuxoki babo le nto abahedeni besithi
  37,152,"“UAllâh Uzele”, bona ngamaxoki okwenene"
  37,153,Ingaba Yena Uzikhethele iintombi kusini na endaweni yoonyana
  37,154,Yintoni na ngani? Nigweba njani kanye
  37,155,Kanti aniqaphelisisi na
  37,156,Okanye mhlawumbi ninegunya elicacileyo nina
  37,157,Yizani nencwadi yenu kaloku ukuba ninenyaniso
  37,158,"Kananjalo baye baqamba ukuhlobana phakathi kwaKhe neeJinni, kodwa zona iiJinni ziyazi (kakuhle) okokuba ziza kuma (phambi kwaKhe ziphendule ngezenzo zazo)"
  37,159,"Uzuko\tlonke\tmalube\tkuAllâh!\t(Okude\tlee)\tkoko bakwayamanisa naYe"
  37,160,"Ngaphandle kwezicaka zika-Allâh, Awazikhethayo"
  37,161,Ngoko ke inene nina bahedeni ndawonye nabo nibanqulayo (izinyanya)
  37,162,Abangekhe balahlekise (nabani na kumakholwa) bamwexule kuYe (uAllâh)
  37,163,Ngaphandle kwalowo umiselwe ukuba atshe esiHogweni
  37,164,Yaye akukho namnye kuthi (ingelosi) koko unendawo yakhe eyaziwayo
  37,165,Kananjalo thina (zingelosi) sima ngokwemigca (sithandaze phambi koAllah)
  37,166,Yaye futhi thina (zingelosi) inene singabo bazukisa uAllâh
  37,167,Kananjalo bona (abahedeni) babedla ngokuthi
  37,168,“Ukuba sasibe naye umlumkisi njengabantu bamandulo
  37,169,Sasiya kuba zizicaka zika-Allâh ezikhethiweyo
  37,170,Kodwa (ngoku i’Kur’ân ifikile) abakholwa kuyo. Ngoko ke baza kwazi
  37,171,"Inene lona ilizwi leThu sele liphumile, kwamandulo mayela neziCaka zeThu abaProfeti"
  37,172,Elokuba ngabo ngokwenene abaza kuba noloyiso
  37,173,Kwanokuba imikhosi yeThu yiyo eza kuba yeyoyisayo
  37,174,Shenxa ke kubo (wena Muhammad) okwethutyana
  37,175,Ubajonge yaye baza kusibona (isohlwayo)
  37,176,Ingaba bafuna ukuba isohlwayo sikhawuleziswe
  37,177,"Ke kaloku ukuhla kwaso singena emizini yabo, iya kuba mbi intsasa (yaloo mini) kwabo babelunyukisiwe"
  37,178,Ngoko ke (wena Muhammad) bashiye okwethutyana
  37,179,"Ubajonge, yaye baza kubona (isohlwayo)"
  37,180,"Uzuko lonke malube seNkosini yakho, iNkosi yobunganga namandla (Ekude lee) koko bakwayamanisa naYo"
  37,181,Uxolo malube kubaThunywa
  37,182,"Neendumiso zonke mazibe kuAllâh, iNkosi uMlondolozi wamazwe"